  <p>Stevens <a id="TSJN-01-03-0610-kw-0001" class="keywordref" title="jump to several favours of July 16. 21. and 22. in text" href="#TSJN-01-03-0610-ks-0901">several favours of July 16. 21. and 22.</a> are all missing, unless that of the 21st is Stevens letter to Gates; see <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-03-02-0579" class="document">Gates to TJ, 21 July</a>.</p></div>
